<text><loc_59><loc_386><loc_441><loc_401>Thus, F ( M 1 ) = { a } . Then by positive involvement and resolvability, F ( M 4 ) = { a } . But F ( M 5 ) = { d } by Lemma 2, so by positive involvement, d ∈ F ( M 4 ) , contradicting F ( M 4 ) = { a } .</text>
